Well, I consider myself a &quot;Psychic&quot; too I use a &quot;monitor Technique not unlike the CIA was said to employ (I discovered it on my own and later read that the CIA was using a similar method)  I use a &quot;monitor&quot; or person to ask questions and I find I can reply psychically  It involves not using the &quot;questioning/judgemental&quot;  part of my brain and staying in the &quot;declaritive mode&quot;--somehow THAT holds the psychic &quot;conduit&quot; open and I can function as a medium.  The monitor person asks the questions and the replies come.  Should I ask the question myself, however, the conduit shuts.  It IS interesting though, I can ask questions indirectly, staying in declaritive mode, by saying to my monitor something like &quot;ask me to look at the flag or ask me what color is his coat---The monitor asks and THEN I get my answer--I stay concious, but with a slight &quot;buzz&quot; and often the info does not go to my long term memory. 

My suggestions on how the boxes work are based on my own years of experience with random viewing fields.  once it became obvious how THEY worked, it was a simple thing to see the correspondence with audio factor in boxes.  One thing the boxes have taught me, however, is that it is NOT &quot;all in the head&quot; as these sound files can be shared with others.---This is making me rethink that my VIDEO random feild stuff may also not be &quot;in the head, and perhaps may be captured on imagery. 

